<DATELINE>QUEBEC CITY (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   One person was missing and nine were rescued
Wednesday after a Canadian coastal vessel and a Great Lakes
freighter collided in the St. Lawrence River 100 miles north of
Quebec City, Canada's coast guard said.
