<NOTE>For Release Weekend Editions, June 18-19, and Thereafter</NOTE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Here are Broadway's new and current shows.
Ticket supply as of June 17 is indicated as Difficult or Available.
Credit card holno and the Paycock,'' Sean O'Casey's classic play revived
by the Gate Theater of Dublin. Now in previews, opens June 21.
